WEBVTT

00:00:10.927 --> 00:00:21.705 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
When the wind blows,
When the rain comes,

00:00:21.705 --> 00:00:31.181 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When the ground beneath you
starts to slip away,

00:00:31.181 --> 00:00:43.026 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God is always near.
And he cares for you.

00:00:43.026 --> 00:00:49.933 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You’re not alone.
Your friends are here.

00:00:49.933 --> 00:00:56.606 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll help you find your way.

00:00:56.606 --> 00:01:03.313 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We won’t forget you.

00:01:03.313 --> 00:01:15.725 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are your family.
We won’t ignore you.

00:01:15.725 --> 00:01:25.602 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We will not fail to see.
We’ll take your hand.

00:01:25.602 --> 00:01:35.245 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll help you stand.
We’ll help you carry on.

00:01:35.245 --> 00:01:46.422 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We won’t forget you.
We are your family.

00:01:53.630 --> 00:02:04.407 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
When the storm’s gone,
When the day breaks,

00:02:04.407 --> 00:02:14.184 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When our love surrounds you
like a warm embrace,

00:02:14.184 --> 00:02:26.496 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Then you come to know
That it’s really so.

00:02:26.496 --> 00:02:32.635 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love is a bond,
A perfect bond,

00:02:32.635 --> 00:02:38.842 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That time will not erase.

00:02:38.842 --> 00:02:45.081 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We won’t forget you.

00:02:45.081 --> 00:02:58.328 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are your family.
We won’t ignore you.

